{"tid":2175544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我一直唔明白中國人呢個民族點解會咁？","createTime":"2020-08-26T14:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T14:03:33.000Z","uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0707238f5e9119af1b7a456988d87218ede2c4b0","tid":2175544,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:00:17.000Z","msg":"一班畜牲走去奶共，為嘅係錢同名氣，呢樣我明。<br />\n<br />\n一班走狗搵完人仔之後，走去外國過日子，我都明。<br />\n<br />\n我就係唔明，點解你去到西方國家，享受人地嘅自由空氣，唔受支那控制，你都可以走去大叫中國萬歲，我愛中國？<br />\n<br />\n你中國人口口聲聲話自己討厭政治，不想扯上政治問題。你本可以安安心心過日子，不問世事，得閒做下運動，讀下書咁。但點解會戰狼上身？<br />\n<br />\n真撚人渣嘅係，有d人有幾本護照，外國有物業，你仲可以叫人地要愛國，唔好移民，會有歧視。真係痴線，咁你又移民？你仔女又係果度讀書？<br />\n<br />\n點解呢班中國人可以咁離奇？完全了解唔到佢地嘅思維邏輯係咩。共匪都可以了解，但佢底下班人們真係令人費解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7f9c4fb30f0ae986a3b650a412cba2ce7f9170","tid":2175544,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60f98c72588d9474daf2b46d195e7f9337ba3b9f","tid":2175544,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd7f9c4fb30f0ae986a3b650a412cba2ce7f9170","tid":2175544,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bb1799e566299d654d2c5b0038dcc4ce5321b72","tid":2175544,"uid":356385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T14:03:33.000Z","msg":"幾時冇p牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}